[{"Code":"en","Title":"Duitnow Pay","Slug":"duitnow-pay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbodw-c083zf-096\"><strong>Private notes</strong></p><h1 data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-bjyf1a-099\" data-start=\"103\" data-end=\"137\">DuitNow Pay Activation Process</h1><h2 data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-lcqv32-100\" data-start=\"139\" data-end=\"152\">Overview</h2><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-b9a0iu-101\" data-start=\"153\" data-end=\"245\">This document describes the step-by-step process for activating DuitNow Pay for merchants.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-osrnh7-102\" data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"273\">Activation Steps</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-42uhg4-103\" data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"300\">1. Merchant Request</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-ykfkah-104\" data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"385\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-gs48dp-105\" data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"385\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-3jo9jo-106\" data-start=\"303\" data-end=\"385\">Merchant submits a request to <strong>Customer Support (CS)</strong> to activate DuitNow Pay.</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-aen1nf-107\" data-start=\"387\" data-end=\"417\">2. CS Request Submission</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-1wnhfa-108\" data-start=\"418\" data-end=\"587\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-s39ahg-109\" data-start=\"418\" data-end=\"498\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-znyh8o-110\" data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"498\">CS creates a request in <strong>#mo-request</strong> Slack channel (Merchant Operations).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-bc95u9-111\" data-start=\"499\" data-end=\"587\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-v7jolw-112\" data-start=\"501\" data-end=\"587\">Request should include merchant details (e.g., MID, business name, contact details).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-brz744-113\" data-start=\"589\" data-end=\"616\">3. MO Query Execution</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-uz02p0-114\" data-start=\"617\" data-end=\"872\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-tgtopl-115\" data-start=\"617\" data-end=\"872\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-6bqk47-116\" data-start=\"619\" data-end=\"872\">Merchant Operations (MO) runs the following <strong>Databricks query</strong> to retrieve the merchant list and details:<br type=\"inline\"> 👉 <a href=\"https://xendit-prod.cloud.databricks.com/editor/queries/599232713215628?o=3626732626433765&amp;contextId=sql-editor\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"decorated-link\" data-start=\"734\" data-end=\"870\">Databricks Query Link</a></p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-mb65vv-118\" data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"899\">4. Data Preparation</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-eiju90-119\" data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"1111\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-dg8xkh-120\" data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"948\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-p6o7f1-121\" data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"948\">Export the query result into <strong>CSV format</strong> following this template <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uYDMrpAw5wFr33hojCGaY6Tt2bMvfmn7QGNOP1F0K7I/edit?gid=1773529663#gid=1773529663\" translate=\"no\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uYDMrpAw5wFr33hojCGaY6Tt2bMvfmn7QGNOP1F0K7I/edit?gid=1773529663#gid=1773529663</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-8n53yv-122\" data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"1111\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-ihquy8-123\" data-start=\"951\" data-end=\"1042\">Fill in column <strong>Segment</strong> and <strong>Industry sector</strong> according to DuitNow’s official sector classification.</p><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-q7y7sw-124\" data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1111\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-mtvlhe-125\" data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1111\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-1thvr6-126\" data-start=\"1047\" data-end=\"1111\">Reference: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gyIuHEzMomeT8kDo9VHbKtqd-z-x0h-0G09iauCz9j8/edit?gid=1094695320#gid=1094695320\" translate=\"no\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gyIuHEzMomeT8kDo9VHbKtqd-z-x0h-0G09iauCz9j8/edit?gid=1094695320#gid=1094695320</a></p></li></ul></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-bc1iuf-127\" data-start=\"1113\" data-end=\"1142\">5. Submission to PayNet</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-7v6j0n-128\" data-start=\"1143\" data-end=\"1443\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-zpl3wc-129\" data-start=\"1143\" data-end=\"1229\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-txkkxv-130\" data-start=\"1145\" data-end=\"1229\">Once the CSV is prepared and validated, MO upload the CSV file to Paynet portal</p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-yfhjyu-131\" data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1443\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-qtqgd6-132\" data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1276\">Email should follow the standard template:</p><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-b5b8ev-133\" data-start=\"1279\" data-end=\"1443\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-9ytrum-134\" data-start=\"1279\" data-end=\"1334\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-o970aw-135\" data-start=\"1281\" data-end=\"1334\">Subject: <code data-start=\"1290\" data-end=\"1332\">DuitNow Pay Activation – &lt;Merchant Name&gt;</code></p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-x85to3-136\" data-start=\"1337\" data-end=\"1387\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-250cmn-137\" data-start=\"1339\" data-end=\"1387\">Attachment: CSV file containing merchant data.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-q44p33-138\" data-start=\"1390\" data-end=\"1443\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-fwi1sp-139\" data-start=\"1392\" data-end=\"1443\">Recipients: PayNet activation team email address.</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-8xkin2-140\" data-start=\"1445\" data-end=\"1473\">6. Credential Handling</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-shri3a-141\" data-start=\"1474\" data-end=\"1651\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0n-2ibilo-142\" data-start=\"1474\" data-end=\"1558\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0n-26lw2i-143\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1558\">PayNet will respond with <strong>merchant credentials</strong> after activation is processed.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0n-tzzrey-144\" data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"1651\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0n-z1pp3z-145\" data-start=\"1561\" data-end=\"1651\">MO receives the credentials and submits them into <strong>Retool</strong> for merchant configuration.</p></li></ul></section><p data-block-id=\"memsbodw-mk040a-098\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mems3297-8yb3nx-001\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Duitnow Pay","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Duitnow Pay","Slug":"duitnow-pay","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Duitnow Pay","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"Duitnow Pay","Slug":"duitnow-pay","ContentType":2,"Content":null,"SeoTitle":"Duitnow Pay","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Duitnow Pay","Slug":"duitnow-pay","ContentType":2,"Content":"<section class=\"internal-notes\" data-permitted-all-team-members=\"true\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbodw-c083zf-096\"><strong>Private notes</strong></p><h1 data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-bjyf1a-099\" data-start=\"103\" data-end=\"137\">DuitNow Pay Activation Process</h1><h2 data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-lcqv32-100\" data-start=\"139\" data-end=\"152\">Overview</h2><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-b9a0iu-101\" data-start=\"153\" data-end=\"245\">This document describes the step-by-step process for activating DuitNow Pay for merchants.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-osrnh7-102\" data-start=\"252\" data-end=\"273\">Activation Steps</h2><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-42uhg4-103\" data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"300\">1. Merchant Request</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-ykfkah-104\" data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"385\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-gs48dp-105\" data-start=\"301\" data-end=\"385\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0k-3jo9jo-106\" data-start=\"303\" data-end=\"385\">Merchant submits a request to <strong>Customer Support (CS)</strong> to activate DuitNow Pay.</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-aen1nf-107\" data-start=\"387\" data-end=\"417\">2. CS Request Submission</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-1wnhfa-108\" data-start=\"418\" data-end=\"587\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-s39ahg-109\" data-start=\"418\" data-end=\"498\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-znyh8o-110\" data-start=\"420\" data-end=\"498\">CS creates a request in <strong>#mo-request</strong> Slack channel (Merchant Operations).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-bc95u9-111\" data-start=\"499\" data-end=\"587\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-v7jolw-112\" data-start=\"501\" data-end=\"587\">Request should include merchant details (e.g., MID, business name, contact details).</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-brz744-113\" data-start=\"589\" data-end=\"616\">3. MO Query Execution</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-uz02p0-114\" data-start=\"617\" data-end=\"872\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-tgtopl-115\" data-start=\"617\" data-end=\"872\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0l-6bqk47-116\" data-start=\"619\" data-end=\"872\">Merchant Operations (MO) runs the following <strong>Databricks query</strong> to retrieve the merchant list and details:<br type=\"inline\"> 👉 <a href=\"https://xendit-prod.cloud.databricks.com/editor/queries/599232713215628?o=3626732626433765&amp;contextId=sql-editor\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"decorated-link\" data-start=\"734\" data-end=\"870\">Databricks Query Link</a></p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-mb65vv-118\" data-start=\"874\" data-end=\"899\">4. Data Preparation</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-eiju90-119\" data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"1111\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-dg8xkh-120\" data-start=\"900\" data-end=\"948\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-p6o7f1-121\" data-start=\"902\" data-end=\"948\">Export the query result into <strong>CSV format</strong> following this template <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uYDMrpAw5wFr33hojCGaY6Tt2bMvfmn7QGNOP1F0K7I/edit?gid=1773529663#gid=1773529663\" translate=\"no\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1uYDMrpAw5wFr33hojCGaY6Tt2bMvfmn7QGNOP1F0K7I/edit?gid=1773529663#gid=1773529663</a></p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-8n53yv-122\" data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"1111\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-ihquy8-123\" data-start=\"951\" data-end=\"1042\">Fill in column <strong>Segment</strong> and <strong>Industry sector</strong> according to DuitNow’s official sector classification.</p><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-q7y7sw-124\" data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1111\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-mtvlhe-125\" data-start=\"1045\" data-end=\"1111\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-1thvr6-126\" data-start=\"1047\" data-end=\"1111\">Reference: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gyIuHEzMomeT8kDo9VHbKtqd-z-x0h-0G09iauCz9j8/edit?gid=1094695320#gid=1094695320\" translate=\"no\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1gyIuHEzMomeT8kDo9VHbKtqd-z-x0h-0G09iauCz9j8/edit?gid=1094695320#gid=1094695320</a></p></li></ul></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-bc1iuf-127\" data-start=\"1113\" data-end=\"1142\">5. Submission to PayNet</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-7v6j0n-128\" data-start=\"1143\" data-end=\"1443\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-zpl3wc-129\" data-start=\"1143\" data-end=\"1229\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-txkkxv-130\" data-start=\"1145\" data-end=\"1229\">Once the CSV is prepared and validated, MO upload the CSV file to Paynet portal</p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-yfhjyu-131\" data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1443\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-qtqgd6-132\" data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1276\">Email should follow the standard template:</p><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-b5b8ev-133\" data-start=\"1279\" data-end=\"1443\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-9ytrum-134\" data-start=\"1279\" data-end=\"1334\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-o970aw-135\" data-start=\"1281\" data-end=\"1334\">Subject: <code data-start=\"1290\" data-end=\"1332\">DuitNow Pay Activation – &lt;Merchant Name&gt;</code></p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-x85to3-136\" data-start=\"1337\" data-end=\"1387\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-250cmn-137\" data-start=\"1339\" data-end=\"1387\">Attachment: CSV file containing merchant data.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-q44p33-138\" data-start=\"1390\" data-end=\"1443\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-fwi1sp-139\" data-start=\"1392\" data-end=\"1443\">Recipients: PayNet activation team email address.</p></li></ul></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-8xkin2-140\" data-start=\"1445\" data-end=\"1473\">6. Credential Handling</h3><ul data-block-id=\"memsbq0m-shri3a-141\" data-start=\"1474\" data-end=\"1651\"><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0n-2ibilo-142\" data-start=\"1474\" data-end=\"1558\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0n-26lw2i-143\" data-start=\"1476\" data-end=\"1558\">PayNet will respond with <strong>merchant credentials</strong> after activation is processed.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"memsbq0n-tzzrey-144\" data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"1651\"><p data-block-id=\"memsbq0n-z1pp3z-145\" data-start=\"1561\" data-end=\"1651\">MO receives the credentials and submits them into <strong>Retool</strong> for merchant configuration.</p></li></ul></section><p data-block-id=\"memsbodw-mk040a-098\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mems3297-8yb3nx-001\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Duitnow Pay","Description":null}]